headline: Assessing Workday Stock After Cloud Partnerships and Recent 11% Pullback in 2025
summary: Wondering if now is the right moment to dive into Workday stock? If you are curious about whether the current price offers good value, you are not alone. The share price has slipped by 0.9% over the past week and is down 7.2% for the last month, contributing to an 11.1% drop year-to-date. However, it is still up by nearly 50% in the past three years.
